11th Last night the raids came off neither of them were successful the 4th Battalion got held up by the wire which was not sufficiently smashed a few of them got in they brought back 2 prisoners had 6 casualties, they reckon if Fritzs bombs had been any good he would have wiped them all out for they fell like a hail storm all round them while they were cutting the wire.
